\hat\phi
x^2 - x - 1 = 0
\phi = \frac{1 + \sqrt{5}}{2},\ \ \ \ \ \hat\phi = \frac{1 - \sqrt{5}}{2}
\phi + \hat\phi = 1,\ \ \ \ \phi\hat\phi = \frac{1-5}{4} = -1
